  OpenIPSL.Electrical.Solar.PowerFactory.DigSILENT.CurrentLimiter currentLimiter(Deadband = Deadband, maxAbsCur = maxAbsCur, maxIq = maxIq, i_EEG = i_EEG)  annotation(
